ZH: 越是挫折，我越能坚强。
EN: The more setbacks I face, the stronger I become.

ZH: 越努力，越有可能实现目标。
EN: The harder you work, the more likely you are to achieve your goals.

ZH: 越困难，越需要团结一致。
EN: The more difficult things get, the more important it is to stay united.

ZH: 越挑战，越能突破自我。
EN: The greater the challenge, the more you can break through yourself.

ZH: 越远，越珍惜家乡的美好。
EN: The further away you are, the more you treasure the beauty of your hometown.

ZH: 越快越好。
EN: The faster, the better.

ZH: 越胖越不好看。
EN: The fatter you are, the less attractive you look.

ZH: 越早开始，越能取得好成绩。
EN: The earlier you start, the better your results will be.

ZH: 越吵越烦。
EN: The more noise, the more annoying.

ZH: 越简单越好。
EN: The simpler, the better.

ZH: 越慢越稳妥。
EN: The slower, the more cautious.

ZH: 越信任，越容易被欺骗。
EN: The more trust, the easier it is to be deceived.

ZH: 越早醒，越有精神。
EN: The earlier you wake up, the more energetic you'll be.

ZH: 越早准备，越有把握。
EN: The earlier you prepare, the more confident you'll be.

ZH: 越好越贵。
EN: The better, the more expensive.

ZH: 越用功，越有收获。
EN: The harder you work, the more you gain.

ZH: 越高兴，越容易原谅别人。
EN: The happier you are, the easier it is to forgive others.

ZH: 越谨慎，越不容易犯错。
EN: The more cautious you are, the less likely you are to make mistakes.

ZH: 越冷越需要保暖。
EN: The colder it is, the more you need to keep warm.

ZH: 越等越失去机会。
EN: The longer you wait, the more opportunities you lose.
